---
/* Skills section - All skills restored, images removed */
---

<section class="box skills">
    <div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4 card">
        <div class="icon-container">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="url(#green-gradient)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline points="4 17 10 11 4 5"></polyline>
                <line x1="12" y1="19" x2="20" y2="19"></line>
                <defs>
                    <linearGradient id="green-gradient" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
                        <stop offset="0%" stop-color="var(--accent-light)" />
                        <stop offset="100%" stop-color="var(--accent-regular)" />
                    </linearGradient>
                </defs>
            </svg>
        </div>
        <h2>Software</h2>
        <p>Expertise in computational analysis, embedded systems, and general purpose programming.</p>
        <div class="tag-group">
            <span class="tag">MS Excel</span>
            <span class="tag">MATLAB</span>
            <span class="tag">Arduino</span>
            <span class="tag">Altium Designer</span>
            <span class="tag">C++</span>
            <span class="tag">Python</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4 card">
        <div class="icon-container">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="url(#green-gradient)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"></path>
                <polyline points="3.27 6.96 12 12.01 20.73 6.96"></polyline>
                <line x1="12" y1="22.08" x2="12" y2="12"></line>
            </svg>
        </div>
        <h2>CAD</h2>
        <p>Advanced 3D modeling, parametric design, and drafting for mechanical engineering.</p>
        <div class="tag-group">
            <span class="tag">SolidWorks</span>
            <span class="tag">Onshape</span>
            <span class="tag">Fusion 360</span>
            <span class="tag">AutoCAD</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4 card">
        <div class="icon-container">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="url(#green-gradient)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"></circle>
                <path d="M19.4 15a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 .33 1.82l.06.06a2 2 0 0 1 0 2.83 2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0l-.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82-.33 1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1 1.51V21a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 9 19.4a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82.33l-.06.06a2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0 2 2 0 0 1 0-2.83l.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 .33-1.82 1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51-1H3a2 2 0 0 1-2-2 2 2 0 0 1 2-2h.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 4.6 9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-.33-1.82l-.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 0-2.83 2 2 0 0 1 2.83 0l.06.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.82.33H9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1-1.51V3a2 2 0 0 1 2-2 2 2 0 0 1 2 2v.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1 1.51 1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.82-.33l.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 2.83 0 2 2 0 0 1 0 2.83l-.06.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-.33 1.82V9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.51 1H21a2 2 0 0 1 2 2 2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51 1z"></path>
            </svg>
        </div>
        <h2>Machining</h2>
        <p>Comprehensive hands-on experience in rapid prototyping and traditional shop tools.</p>
        <div class="tag-group">
            <span class="tag">3D Printing</span>
            <span class="tag">Laser Cutting</span>
            <span class="tag">CNC Milling</span>
            <span class="tag">Drill Press</span>
            <span class="tag">Band Saw</span>
            <span class="tag">Lathe</span>
            <span class="tag">Waterjet Cutting</span>
            <span class="tag">Soldering</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .box {
        border: 1px solid var(--gray-800);
        border-radius: 0.75rem;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        background-color: var(--gray-999_40);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }

    .skills {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 3rem;
    }

    .card {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
    }

    .icon-container {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .skills h2 {
        font-size: var(--text-lg);
        color: var(--gray-100);
    }

    .skills p {
        color: var(--gray-400);
        font-size: var(--text-sm);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .tag-group {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        margin-top: auto;
    }

    .tag {
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        padding: 0.25rem 0.6rem;
        background: var(--gray-800);
        color: var(--gray-200);
        border-radius: 0.375rem;
        border: 1px solid var(--gray-700);
    }

    @media (min-width: 50em) {
        .box {
            border-radius: 1.5rem;
            padding: 2.5rem;
        }

        .skills {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 5rem;
        }

        .skills h2 {
            font-size: var(--text-2xl);
        }
    }
</style>